### Get all transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions


### Get transaction
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/6885269d7a1041cd19651114


### Add new transaction
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 1500,
  "category": "Salary",
  "account": "bank",
  "description": "salary june 2025"
}


### Update a transaction
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/6885269d7a1041cd19651114
